'''赫伯特·理查德·“赫布”·鲍迈斯特'''（{{lang-en|Herbert Richard "Herb" Baumeister}}，{{bd|1947年|4月7日|1996年|7月3日}}），[[美国|美国]][[連環殺手|连环杀人案]]嫌犯。鲍迈斯特是[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[韋斯特菲爾德_(印地安納州)|韦斯特菲尔德]]人，因在1990年代初谋杀了十多名男子而受到调查，其中大多数受害者都是在[[同志酒吧|同性恋酒吧]]最后一次被人看见。警方在鲍迈斯特的农场中发现11具尸体，其中8人身份已被确认。<ref name="auto1">{{Cite news|author=Higgins|first=Will|title=House with dark past fulfills family's dream|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146336/chillicothe_gazette/|accessdate=June 21, 2018|work={{tsl|en|Chillicothe Gazette||Chillicothe Gazette}}|date=October 30, 2012|page=4A|via=Newspapers.com|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621070008/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146336/chillicothe_gazette/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{Cite news|author=Mitchell|first=Dawn|title=Retro Indy: Heinous crimes of serial killers in Indiana|url=http://www.indystar.com/wlna/news/history/retroindy/2014/09/12/indiana-serial-killers/15402833/|accessdate=January 12, 2017|work=The Indianapolis Star|date=February 29, 2016}}</ref>逮捕令发出后，鲍迈斯特逃到[[加拿大|加拿大]]自杀。后来他又被指控杀害至少9名男子。

== 早年生活 ==
鲍迈斯特生于[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[印第安納波利斯|印第安纳波利斯]]，父母分别是赫伯特和伊丽莎白。鲍迈斯特家有四个孩子，他是长子。<ref name="People1996">{{Cite journal|title=While Julie Was Away|url=http://people.com/archive/while-julie-was-away-vol-46-no-26/|last=Jerome|first=Richard|last2=Weinstein|first2=Fannie|date=December 23, 1996|journal=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]|accessdate=January 17, 2015|issue=26|volume=46|issn=0093-7673|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507100120/https://people.com/archive/while-julie-was-away-vol-46-no-26/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Longtime anesthesiologist Herbert E. Baumeister dies|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146233/the_indianapolis_star/|accessdate=June 21, 2018|work=The Indianapolis Star|date=November 13, 1986|page=48|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621070010/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146233/the_indianapolis_star/|dead-url=no}} {{Free access}}</ref>他童年时很正常，到[[青少年|青春期]]开始表现出[[反社會行為|反社会行为]]。鲍迈斯特曾把玩死去的动物，也曾在老师的桌子上撒尿。他被诊断出患有[[精神分裂症|精神分裂症]] ，但并未接受进一步的治疗。<ref name="Albert">{{Cite web|title=Herb Baumeister "The I-70 Strangler"|url=http://maamodt.asp.radford.edu/Psyc%20405/serial%20killers/Baumeister,%20Herb%20-%20fall,%202005.pdf|accessdate=|author=Sherri Armistead|date=|work=|publisher=Department of Psychology, Radford University|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215064202/http://maamodt.asp.radford.edu/Psyc%20405/serial%20killers/Baumeister,%20Herb%20-%20fall,%202005.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

1965年，鲍迈斯特在[[印第安纳大学与普渡大学印第安纳波利斯联合分校|印第安纳大学]]读了一个学期后退学，1967年再次返校。<ref name="People1996">{{Cite journal|title=While Julie Was Away|url=http://people.com/archive/while-julie-was-away-vol-46-no-26/|last=Jerome|first=Richard|last2=Weinstein|first2=Fannie|date=December 23, 1996|journal=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]|accessdate=January 17, 2015|issue=26|volume=46|issn=0093-7673}}</ref>1972年，他在[[巴特勒大學|巴特勒大学]]读了一个学期。<ref name="Star15-9-1996">{{Cite news|author=Labalme|first=Jenny|title=Businessman puzzled people in life and death|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146253/the_indianapolis_star/|accessdate=June 21, 2018|work=The Indianapolis Star|date=September 15, 1996|pages=41, 49|via=Newspapers.com|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621070250/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146253/the_indianapolis_star/|dead-url=no}} {{Free access}}</ref>成年后，他从事了许多工作，人们说他有强烈的职业道德感，但行为也越来越离奇。 

鲍迈斯特于1971年11月与朱莉安·塞特结婚，生了三个孩子。<ref name="People1996">{{Cite journal|title=While Julie Was Away|url=http://people.com/archive/while-julie-was-away-vol-46-no-26/|last=Jerome|first=Richard|last2=Weinstein|first2=Fannie|date=December 23, 1996|journal=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]|accessdate=January 17, 2015|issue=26|volume=46|issn=0093-7673}}</ref><ref name="Star15-9-1996">{{Cite news|author=Labalme|first=Jenny|title=Businessman puzzled people in life and death|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146253/the_indianapolis_star/|accessdate=June 21, 2018|work=The Indianapolis Star|date=September 15, 1996|pages=41, 49|via=Newspapers.com}} {{Free access}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Meredith|first=Robyn|title=Seven Skeletons, and a Suburb in Shock|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1996/10/16/us/seven-skeletons-and-a-suburb-in-shock.html|accessdate=January 4, 2017|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=October 16, 1996|archive-date=2020-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606172906/https://www.nytimes.com/1996/10/16/us/seven-skeletons-and-a-suburb-in-shock.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>朱莉安后来说，在过去25年的婚姻生活中，他们只上过六次床。<ref name="Albert">{{Cite web|title=Herb Baumeister "The I-70 Strangler"|url=http://maamodt.asp.radford.edu/Psyc%20405/serial%20killers/Baumeister,%20Herb%20-%20fall,%202005.pdf|accessdate=|author=Sherri Armistead|date=|work=|publisher=Department of Psychology, Radford University}}</ref>1970年代，鲍迈斯特的父亲把他送进了一家精神病医院。鲍迈斯特于1988年在印第安纳波利斯建立了Sav-A-Lot旧货连锁店，有2家门店。 

== 调查 ==
到1990年代初，马里恩县警署和印第安纳波利斯警察局开始调查印第安纳波利斯地区一些年龄、身高和体重相仿的男同性恋者的失踪案件。1992年，一个名叫托尼·哈里斯的男子联系到调查人员，说一个叫布赖恩·斯马特的[[同志酒吧|男同性恋酒吧]]顾客把他的一个朋友杀了，并曾在[[窒息式性愛|窒息式性爱]]时想用水池的软管杀死他。哈里斯于1995年8月再次见到这个人，记下了他的车牌号。<ref name="Albert">{{Cite web|title=Herb Baumeister "The I-70 Strangler"|url=http://maamodt.asp.radford.edu/Psyc%20405/serial%20killers/Baumeister,%20Herb%20-%20fall,%202005.pdf|accessdate=|author=Sherri Armistead|date=|work=|publisher=Department of Psychology, Radford University}}</ref>根据这些信息，警方确认布赖恩·斯马特就是赫布·鲍迈斯特。 

调查人员要求搜查鲍迈斯特的房屋，鲍迈斯特和妻子均拒绝搜查。1996年6月，朱莉安感觉丈夫情绪的波动和行为的不稳定十分可怕，在申请[[离婚|离婚]]后 ，同意调查人员搜查。<ref name="People1996">{{Cite journal|title=While Julie Was Away|url=http://people.com/archive/while-julie-was-away-vol-46-no-26/|last=Jerome|first=Richard|last2=Weinstein|first2=Fannie|date=December 23, 1996|journal=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]|accessdate=January 17, 2015|issue=26|volume=46|issn=0093-7673}}</ref>趁鲍迈斯特在度假时，调查人员搜查了他的面积{{Convert|18|acre|m2}}的农场，发现了11名男子的遗体，其中8人身份已被确认。<ref name="auto1" /><ref name="auto">{{Cite news|author=Mitchell|first=Dawn|title=Retro Indy: Heinous crimes of serial killers in Indiana|url=http://www.indystar.com/wlna/news/history/retroindy/2014/09/12/indiana-serial-killers/15402833/|accessdate=January 12, 2017|work=The Indianapolis Star|date=February 29, 2016}}</ref> 

警方对鲍迈斯特下发逮捕令。鲍迈斯特逃到加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]]后，在[[休伦湖|休伦湖]]Pinery省立公园开枪自杀。他在[[遺書|遗书]]中声称自己自杀的原因是婚姻和事业两方面的失败，<ref>{{Cite news|author=Labalme|first=Jenny|title=Suicide note mentions marriage, business but not bones|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146358/the_indianapolis_star/|accessdate=June 21, 2018|work=[[The_Indianapolis_Star|The Indianapolis Star]]|date=July 6, 1996|pages=1–2|via=Newspapers.com|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621070000/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21146358/the_indianapolis_star/|dead-url=no}} {{Free access}}</ref>不承认发现的那些人是被他谋杀的。 <ref name="People1996">{{Cite journal|title=While Julie Was Away|url=http://people.com/archive/while-julie-was-away-vol-46-no-26/|last=Jerome|first=Richard|last2=Weinstein|first2=Fannie|date=December 23, 1996|journal=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]|accessdate=January 17, 2015|issue=26|volume=46|issn=0093-7673}}</ref> 

鲍迈斯特死后又涉嫌杀害其他9个人，尸体于20世纪80年代初至中期在印第安纳波利斯和[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[哥伦布_(俄亥俄州)|哥伦布]]之间的[[70號州際公路|70号州际公路]]沿线农村地区发现。一位目击者称鲍迈斯特于1983年与迈克尔·赖利一起离开酒吧，后来赖利被杀害。和其他死者一样，赖利被勒死，尸体被脱掉衣服后扔在河中。 <ref>{{Cite news|title=Indiana Businessman Is Linked To 9 Other Killings of Men|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/29/us/indiana-businessman-is-linked-to-9-other-killings-of-men.html|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|work=The New York Times|date=April 29, 1998|accessdate=January 4, 2017|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510200334/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/29/us/indiana-businessman-is-linked-to-9-other-killings-of-men.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

